reviewText: Two great episodes of one of the greatest shows in tv history!

This tape contains 2 episodes from the 3rd season of Flipper, the classic TV series about a pet dolphin, which is not available on DVD. In Flipper and the Puppy a diver's boat catches on fire so he puts his puppy in a floating tub.  Flipper takes care of the puppy, while the man, with the bends, is rescued.  In Flipper and the Seal, Martin Sheen guest stars as a drifter falsely accused of stealing mussels; only Flipper knows the real culprit is a seal.
